markdown_description:
## Effects of mutations to rabies G on escape from antibody 17C7

Pseudovirus deep mutational scanning of how mutations to rabies G affect
neutralization by antibody 17C7 shown on prefusion structure with antibody (8a1e).


Structure shown is from PDB 8a1e.

Study by Arjun Aditham, Caelan Radford, Caleb Carr, and Jesse Bloom (2024).
See [https://github.com/dms-vep/RABV_Pasteur_G_DMS](https://github.com/dms-vep/RABV_Pasteur_G_DMS) for code.
